init_text: A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She's unaware that she's actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who's fallen for her, and is certain he's going to get it right this time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It didn't matter whether it was a blind date or not, though, because they all ended up being the same.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She felt like she was always giving the same answers too.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Was it possible that she had been dating the same guy over and over again?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: That night, she was meeting a guy who had just moved to the city, and he didn't know anybody.
